vernac_cmds: Definition add_part (A : part_set E) (x : E) := union A (single x).
Lemma add_part_comp : forall (A A' : part_set E) (x x' : E), Equal A A' -> Equal x x' -> Equal (add_part A x) (add_part A' x').
unfold add_part in |- *; auto with algebra.
Lemma add_part_in : forall (A : part_set E) (x : E), in_part x (add_part A x).
Lemma add_part_com : forall (A : part_set E) (x y : E), Equal (add_part (add_part A x) y) (add_part (add_part A y) x).
apply Trans with (union A (union (single x) (single y))); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (union A (union (single y) (single x))); auto with algebra.
Lemma add_in : forall (A : part_set E) (x : E), in_part x A -> Equal (add_part A x) A.
simpl in |- *; unfold pred_compatible, eq_part, in_part in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Lemma add_part_in_el_diff : forall (A : part_set E) (x y : E), in_part y (add_part A x) -> ~ Equal y x -> in_part y A.
unfold eq_part, add_part, union, single in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Lemma add_part_in_el_not_in : forall (A : part_set E) (x y : E), in_part y (add_part A x) -> ~ in_part y A -> Equal y x.
unfold eq_part, add_part, union, single in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Lemma add_part_simpl : forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x A -> ~ in_part x B -> Equal (add_part A x) (add_part B x) -> Equal A B.
case A; case B; simpl in |- *.
unfold eq_part, add_part, union, single in |- *; simpl in |- *.
apply pa with x; auto with algebra.
apply pb with x0; auto with algebra.
apply pa with x0; auto with algebra.
absurd (Equal x0 x); auto with algebra.
absurd (Equal x0 x); auto with algebra.
Definition minus_part (A : part_set E) (x : E) := diff A (single x).
Lemma minus_part_comp : forall (A A' : part_set E) (x x' : E), Equal A A' -> Equal x x' -> Equal (minus_part A x) (minus_part A' x').
unfold minus_part in |- *; auto with algebra.
Lemma minus_part_not_in : forall (A : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x (minus_part A x).
Lemma minus_part_com : forall (A : part_set E) (x y : E), Equal (minus_part (minus_part A x) y) (minus_part (minus_part A y) x).
unfold eq_part, diff, single in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Lemma minus_not_in : forall (A : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x A -> Equal (minus_part A x) A.
unfold eq_part, minus_part, diff, single in |- *; simpl in |- *.
case A; unfold pred_compatible in |- *; simpl in |- *.
intros a pa x neg_a_x x0.
Lemma minus_trans_not_in : forall (A : part_set E) (x y : E), ~ in_part y A -> ~ in_part y (minus_part A x).
unfold eq_part, minus_part, diff, single in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Lemma union_unit_l : forall A : part_set E, Equal (union (empty E) A) A.
unfold eq_part, union, empty in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Lemma single_add : forall x : E, Equal (single x) (add_part (empty E) x).
Lemma minus_add : forall (A : part_set E) (x : E), in_part x A -> Equal (add_part (minus_part A x) x) A.
unfold eq_part, add_part, minus_part, union, diff, single in |- *; simpl in |- *.
apply pa with x; auto with algebra.
Lemma add_minus : forall (A : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x A -> Equal (minus_part (add_part A x) x) A.
unfold eq_part, add_part, minus_part, union, diff, single in |- *; simpl in |- *.
apply pa with x0; auto with algebra.

Inductive cardinal : part_set E -> nat -> Prop := | cardinal_empty : forall A : part_set E, Equal A (empty E) -> cardinal A 0 | cardinal_add : forall (A B : part_set E) (n : nat), cardinal B n -> forall x : E, ~ in_part x B -> Equal A (add_part B x) -> cardinal A (S n).
Lemma cardinal_comp : forall (A B : part_set E) (n m : nat), Equal A B -> n = m -> cardinal A n -> cardinal B m.
apply Trans with A; auto with algebra.
apply cardinal_add with B0 x; auto with algebra.
apply Trans with A; auto with algebra.
Lemma cardinal_comp_l : forall (A B : part_set E) (n : nat), Equal A B -> cardinal A n -> cardinal B n.
apply cardinal_comp with A n; auto with algebra.
Lemma cardinal_comp_r : forall (A : part_set E) (n m : nat), n = m -> cardinal A n -> cardinal A m.
apply cardinal_comp with A n; auto with algebra.
Lemma cardinal_single : forall x : E, cardinal (single x) 1.
apply cardinal_add with (empty E) x; auto with algebra.
Lemma cardinal_pair : forall x y : E, ~ Equal x y -> cardinal (union (single x) (single y)) 2.
apply cardinal_add with (single x) y; auto with algebra.
Lemma cardinal_O_empty : forall A : part_set E, cardinal A 0 -> Equal A (empty E).
Lemma cardinal_1_single : forall A : part_set E, cardinal A 1 -> exists x : E, Equal A (single x).
apply Trans with (add_part B x); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (add_part (empty E) x); auto with algebra.
Lemma not_in_empty : forall A : part_set E, (forall x : E, ~ in_part x A) -> Equal A (empty E).
unfold eq_part, empty in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Lemma not_in_part_trans : forall (x : E) (A B : part_set E), ~ in_part x A -> Equal A B -> ~ in_part x B.
case A; case B; simpl in |- *.
Lemma not_in_part_trans_eq : forall (x y : E) (A : part_set E), ~ in_part x A -> Equal x y -> ~ in_part y A.
apply (pa y x); auto with algebra.

Lemma cardinal_sup3 : forall (A B C : part_set E) (x y : E), Equal A (add_part B x) -> Equal A (add_part C y) -> ~ in_part x B -> ~ in_part y C -> ~ Equal x y -> exists D : part_set E, Equal B (add_part D y) /\ Equal C (add_part D x) /\ ~ in_part x D /\ ~ in_part y D.
apply add_part_in_el_diff with x; auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with A; auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with (add_part C y); auto with algebra.
apply add_part_simpl with y; auto with algebra.
absurd (Equal y x); auto with algebra.
apply add_part_in_el_not_in with (minus_part B y); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (add_part (add_part (minus_part B y) y) x); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (add_part B x); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with A; auto with algebra.
apply add_part_in_el_diff with x; auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with (add_part C y); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with A; auto with algebra.

Lemma cardinal_ind2 : forall P : forall (n : nat) (A : part_set E), cardinal A n -> Prop, (forall (A : part_set E) (c : cardinal A 0), P 0 A c) -> (forall n : nat, (forall (B : part_set E) (c : cardinal B n), P n B c) -> forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x B -> Equal A (add_part B x) -> forall c' : cardinal A (S n), P (S n) A c') -> forall (n : nat) (A : part_set E) (c : cardinal A n), P n A c.
apply (H0 n0 H1 A B x H4 H6 c).
Lemma cardinal_S : forall (n : nat) (A B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x B -> Equal A (add_part B x) -> cardinal A (S n) -> cardinal B n.
apply add_part_simpl with x; auto with algebra.
apply not_in_part_trans_eq with x0; auto with algebra.
apply Trans with A; auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (add_part B0 x0); auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with (add_part B0 x0); auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with A; auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with (add_part B x); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (add_part (empty E) x0); auto with algebra.
apply cardinal_comp_l with B0; auto with algebra.
apply add_part_simpl with x; auto with algebra.
apply not_in_part_trans_eq with x0; auto with algebra.
apply Trans with A; auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (add_part B0 x0); auto with algebra.
apply cardinal_add with C x0; auto with algebra.
apply H with B0 x; auto with algebra.
Lemma cardinalO_unique : forall A : part_set E, cardinal A 0 -> forall m : nat, cardinal A m -> 0 = m.
absurd (in_part x (empty E)); auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with A; auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with (add_part B x); auto with algebra.
Lemma cardinal_unique : forall (n : nat) (A : part_set E), cardinal A n -> forall m : nat, cardinal A m -> n = m.
apply cardinal_ind2 with (P := fun (n : nat) (A : part_set E) (c : cardinal A n) => forall m : nat, cardinal A m -> n = m); auto with algebra.
intros n0 H A0 B x H0 H1 c' m.
absurd (in_part x (empty E)); auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with A0; auto with algebra.
apply in_part_comp_r with (add_part B x); auto with algebra.
apply H with B; auto with algebra.
apply cardinal_S with A0 x; auto with algebra.
apply cardinal_S with A0 x; auto with algebra.
